#: ../../development/local-development.md:1 95333fbda5f04f1c8ac954b27f33296f
msgid "Local Development"
msgstr "本地开发"

#: ../../development/local-development.md:3 4c40bd020cbf4d96a7805b0a270f728f
msgid "This guide covers running, debugging, and iterating on NotebookLM locally."
msgstr "本指南介绍如何在本地运行、调试和迭代 NotebookLM。"

#: ../../development/local-development.md:5 6c20a6efbad24cb4b78eded1310095a3
msgid "Starting the Development Server"
msgstr "启动开发服务器"

#: ../../development/local-development.md:11 8be3dfd529714402a115aa2a4f23776f
msgid ""
"This starts the Next.js development server with hot module replacement "
"(HMR). The application is available at **http://localhost:3000**."
msgstr "这将启动带有热模块替换（HMR）的 Next.js 开发服务器。应用程序可通过 **http://localhost:3000** 访问。"

#: ../../development/local-development.md:13 e5dcca6fa5d841d09def16e4c0710b8b
msgid "Development Features"
msgstr "开发特性"

#: ../../development/local-development.md:15 0b7583ff3dff41b38d51c21d69ef5277
msgid "**Hot Reload** — Changes to components and pages are reflected immediately"
msgstr "**热重载** —— 组件和页面的更改会立即生效"

#: ../../development/local-development.md:16 3067693371ff4d25bd9941016f4571f3
msgid ""
"**API Route Reload** — Server-side API changes take effect on the next "
"request"
msgstr "**API 路由重载** —— 服务端 API 更改在下次请求时生效"

#: ../../development/local-development.md:17 62159d07fe8c4af2a8d9b2d41be9167f
msgid ""
"**Error Overlay** — Build errors and runtime errors are displayed in the "
"browser"
msgstr "**错误覆盖层** —— 构建错误和运行时错误会在浏览器中显示"

#: ../../development/local-development.md:19 4016cae4ca8249118d800236fef56da1
msgid "Common Development Tasks"
msgstr "常见开发任务"

#: ../../development/local-development.md:21 61dc2640cc274f60a1b3c36511e0e15f
msgid "Running Type Checks"
msgstr "运行类型检查"

#: ../../development/local-development.md:27 739b3d160cd640508a2015273339fb82
msgid "Running Lint"
msgstr "运行 Lint"

#: ../../development/local-development.md:33 2683d2c65d854896a376a19e03e734af
msgid "Uses ESLint with the project's configured rules."
msgstr "使用 ESLint 及项目配置的规则。"

#: ../../development/local-development.md:35 3457a30d3bef43379742f095ca2415b0
msgid "Building for Production"
msgstr "生产环境构建"

#: ../../development/local-development.md:41 92830f99a8a64b329c4eb2b0ebea775c
msgid "Creates an optimized production build. This also performs type checking."
msgstr "创建优化的生产环境构建。这也会执行类型检查。"

#: ../../development/local-development.md:43 dc47f572878847b68431fda3c400fa13
msgid "Database Operations"
msgstr "数据库操作"

#: ../../development/local-development.md:56 b8511019e7b948658cc305005207533f
msgid "Debugging"
msgstr "调试"

#: ../../development/local-development.md:58 f3d0a118f7894a2b9680b5e53ef7038a
msgid "Server-Side Debugging"
msgstr "服务端调试"

#: ../../development/local-development.md:60 467794f6ef624f04883c5aec0b094194
msgid "Start the dev server with the Node.js inspector:"
msgstr "使用 Node.js 调试器启动开发服务器："

#: ../../development/local-development.md:64 c985bf293a2241c9b0e84aa3e2933b32
msgid "Open `chrome://inspect` in Chrome and connect to the Node.js process"
msgstr "在 Chrome 中打开 `chrome://inspect` 并连接到 Node.js 进程"

#: ../../development/local-development.md:65 a0bf81c0e78143d09cac9281bc8beeba
msgid "Set breakpoints in API routes and server-side code"
msgstr "在 API 路由和服务端代码中设置断点"

#: ../../development/local-development.md:67 8b757f26dbda4e4f8e864a3631834f47
msgid "Client-Side Debugging"
msgstr "客户端调试"

#: ../../development/local-development.md:69 ce69c01f63dd4672a83118bc3c3f6480
msgid "Use the browser's built-in developer tools:"
msgstr "使用浏览器内置的开发者工具："

#: ../../development/local-development.md:70 90125b609d6243619e0abdd83ba00594
msgid "**React DevTools** — Inspect component hierarchy and state"
msgstr "**React DevTools** —— 检查组件层级和状态"

#: ../../development/local-development.md:71 6601201e5ed048fbb364a06ab1c94503
msgid "**Network Tab** — Monitor API requests and responses"
msgstr "**网络选项卡** —— 监控 API 请求和响应"

#: ../../development/local-development.md:72 5f2031a2867d4c63b6e6db8d61a2bc19
msgid "**Console** — View logs and errors"
msgstr "**控制台** —— 查看日志和错误"

#: ../../development/local-development.md:74 5936fbe84f2d43d8a9ddb3395b52bb67
msgid "Environment Setup Tips"
msgstr "环境设置技巧"

#: ../../development/local-development.md:76 198fbca2df5f4323bb03b5ee1535967d
msgid "Without AI API Keys"
msgstr "无 AI API 密钥"

#: ../../development/local-development.md:78 26409111c8ed4274bc7934d6e918d5e3
msgid "You can develop most features without configuring AI API keys:"
msgstr "大部分功能无需配置 AI API 密钥即可开发："

#: ../../development/local-development.md:79 d74ed6821e0d4ba2bfac834a72cd7e0b
msgid ""
"Workspace management, file browser, and UI components work without any "
"API key"
msgstr "工作空间管理、文件浏览器和 UI 组件无需任何 API 密钥即可运行"

#: ../../development/local-development.md:80 dbf9606c9f34425ea9faadbf3608c19a
msgid ""
"AI chat and note generation features will show a \"not configured\" "
"message"
msgstr "AI 对话和笔记生成功能将显示\"未配置\"消息"

#: ../../development/local-development.md:82 d82bd6fe626b4b1dab80e95049cb6100
msgid "Multiple Root Directories"
msgstr "多个根目录"

#: ../../development/local-development.md:84 99a5c94020ef4407bd409961ddc37aea
msgid "For testing workspace management with multiple roots:"
msgstr "用于测试多根目录的工作空间管理："

#: ../../development/local-development.md:90 e744ef1f7b3e42fbb008e40887d38ab3
msgid "Using a Local AI Proxy"
msgstr "使用本地 AI 代理"

#: ../../development/local-development.md:92 5aa896c9faad45488307a86b6b72d5ca
msgid ""
"If you run a local LLM (e.g., via Ollama or LM Studio) with an OpenAI-"
"compatible API:"
msgstr "如果您运行本地 LLM（例如通过 Ollama 或 LM Studio）并提供 OpenAI 兼容 API："
